      "text": [
        ": قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه وآله: من المروءة استصلاح المال"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.dr-ali-peiravi": [
          "1-34 Muhammad ibn Ali Majiluyih - may God be pleased with him - narrated that his uncle Muhammad ibn Abil-Qasim quoted on the authority of Ahmad ibn Aba Abdullah al-Barqy, on the authority of Isma’il ibn Mihran, on the authority of Salih ibn Sa’id, on the authority of Aban ibn Taqlib, on the authority of Abi Ja’far al-Baqir (MGB) that God’s Prophet (MGB) said, ““From chivalry is the improvement of wealth.”.”"
        ]
      }
